# Agile Task Mobile

This is a rhomobile framework application for the AgileTask webservice - agiletask.me

## Getting Started

1. install the rhodes gem "gem install rhodes"
2. install all of the sdks you plan on using for android, iphone etc.
3. run rhodes-setup for you system
4. create a rhodes application - rhodes app AgileTaskMobile
5. fetch the AgileTaskMobile git repository 
6. add your API key for testing in the "Tasks" controller
7. run the app in an emulator example "rake run:android"